0days%20before%20election%20results%2C%20Mr%20Patole's%20claim%20that%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20government%20formed%20after%20the%20election%20would%20be%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20irked%20Team%20Thackeray%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%2C%20who%20said%20he%20would%20not%20accept%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%2C%20however%2C%20showed%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20collapsing%20below%20the%2050%20mark%20as%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20posted%20a%20mammoth%20score%20of%20232.%20The%20Congress%20posted%20its%20worst-ever%20show%20in%20Maharashtra%20election%2C%20its%20tally%20dropping%20from%2044%20in%20the%20last%20election%20to%2016%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Congress%20described%20the%20Maharashtra%20election%20results%20as%20%26quot%3Bunexpected%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binexplicable%26quot%3B.%20Addressing%20the%20media%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20no%20two%20ways%20about%20it%20that%20in%20a%20targeted%20manner%2C%20the%20level-playing%20field%2C%20a%20phrase%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20often%20uses%2C%20was%20disturbed.%20The%20election%20results%20are%20unexpected%2C%20very%20surprising%20and%20inexplicable.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20party%20would%20analyse%20its%20performance%20and%20the%20factors%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732512060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fr366eed_nana-patole_625x300_10_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnana-patole-resigns-as-maharashtra-congress-chief-days-after-assembly-poll-drubbing-7099298%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heads%20have%20started%20rolling%20in%20Maharashtra%20after%20the%20Opposition's%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20took%20a%20massive%20drubbing%20in%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20results%20declared%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnana-patole-resigns-as-maharashtra-congress-chief-days-after-assembly-poll-drubbing-7099298%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Yamandu%20Orsi%2C%20Uruguay's%20Newly-Elected%20'Modern%20Left'%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUruguay's%20new%20president-elect%20Yamandu%20Orsi%2C%20whose%20political%20ambitions%20were%20galvanized%20by%20his%20experience%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20dictatorship%2C%20was%20the%20pollsters'%20narrow%20favorite%20to%20win%20the%20second%20round%20of%20the%20South%20American%20nation's%20presidential%20election%20on%20Sunday%20for%20the%20center-left.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2057-year-old%20former%20history%20teacher%20and%20local%20mayor%20managed%20to%20unseat%20the%20ruling%20conservative%20bloc.%20He%20placed%20first%20with%2049.8%25%20of%20votes%20for%20the%20left-leaning%20Broad%20Front%20coalition%20in%20November's%20second%20round%2C%20against%20Alvaro%20Delgado%20of%20the%20governing%20center-right%20National%20Party%20with%2045.9%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20campaign%2C%20Orsi%20had%20sought%20to%20reassure%20Uruguayans%20that%20he%20did%20not%20plan%20a%20sharp%20political%20shift%20in%20the%20traditionally%20moderate%20and%20relatively%20wealthy%20nation%20of%203.4%20million%20people%20that%20is%20known%20for%20its%20beaches%2C%20legal%20cannabis%20and%20stable%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20concluded%20in%20a%20cordial%20atmosphere%2C%20with%20both%20sides%20vowing%20to%20work%20together%20to%20advance%20the%20nation.%20Delgado%20had%20said%20before%20the%20results%20he%20would%20invite%20Orsi%20over%20for%20traditional%20mate%20tea%20should%20he%20secure%20a%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrsi%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20usher%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20modern%20left%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20tackle%20homelessness%2C%20poverty%20and%20crime%20-%20a%20key%20voter%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHomicide%20rates%20in%20U