%20was%20just%20looking%20for%20a%20big%20flashing%20red%20stop%20button%20that%20I%20could%20slap%20and%20make%20this%20stop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJennifer's%20name%20and%20image%20had%20been%20used%20to%20create%20a%20chatbot%20on%20Character.AI%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20lets%20users%20interact%20with%20AI-generated%20personalities.%20According%20to%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20now-deleted%20profile%2C%20several%20users%20had%20engaged%20with%20the%20digital%20version%20of%20Jennifer%2C%20created%20by%20someone%20on%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrecente%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20nonprofit%20in%20his%20daughter's%20name%20to%20prevent%20teen%20dating%20violence%2C%20was%20horrified%20that%20the%20platform%20allowed%20a%20user%20to%20create%20an%20AI%20facsimile%20of%20a%20murdered%20high%20school%20student%20without%20the%20family's%20consent.%20Experts%20say%20the%20incident%20highlights%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20AI%20industry's%20ability%20to%20protect%20users%20from%20the%20risks%20posed%20by%20technology%20capable%20of%20handling%20sensitive%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20quite%20a%20bit%20for%20me%20to%20be%20shocked%20because%20I%20really%20have%20been%20through%20quite%20a%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20Crecente%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20this%20was%20a%20new%20low.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKathryn%20Kelly%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Character%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20company%20removes%20chatbots%20that%20violate%20its%20terms%20of%20service%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bcontinuously%20evolving%20and%20refining%20our%20safety%20practices%20to%20prioritize%20community%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20notified%20about%20Jennifer's%20Character%2C%20we%20reviewed%20the%20content%20and%20the%20account%2C%20taking%20action%20in%20line%20with%20our%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20company's%20terms%20prohibit%20users%20from%20impersonating%20any%20person%20or%20