20with%20calm%20progress%20as%20they%20entered%20Punjab%20territory.%20However%2C%20police%20deployed%20heavy%20tear%20gas%20near%20key%20checkpoints%20to%20impede%20their%20passage.%20At%20these%20sites%2C%20law%20enforcement%20aimed%20to%20halt%20the%20convoys%2C%20forcing%20the%20PTI%20supporters%20to%20face%20resistance%20before%20they%20could%20continue%20their%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20to%20the%20crowd%2C%20Gandapur%20emphasised%20that%20the%20march%20would%20not%20stop%20until%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20PTI%20founder%2C%20was%20released.%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20advance%20and%20not%20turn%20back%20until%20Imran%20Khan%20is%20released%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared%2C%20rallying%20the%20supporters%20to%20press%20on%20despite%20the%20delays%20caused%20by%20police%20intervention.%20Later%2C%20addressing%20the%20group%20again%20at%20Ghazi%2C%20he%20urged%20them%20to%20prepare%20for%20further%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrepare%2C%20as%20we%20will%20need%20to%20confront%20further%20resistance%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Gandapur%20said%2C%20reinforcing%20the%20commitment%20to%20the%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convoy%2C%20temporarily%20halted%20at%20Ghazi%20Bridge%2C%20faced%20mixed%20reactions%20from%20party%20members%2C%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20Gandapur%20advised%20them%20to%20rest%20before%20further%20confrontations.%20Bushra%20Bibi%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20expressed%20frustration%20at%20the%20delays%2C%20urging%20the%20convoy%20to%20move%20forward%20without%20further%20pause.%20Speaking%20from%20her%20vehicle%2C%20she%20emphasised%2C%20%26quot%3BTime%20is%20being%20wasted%2C%26quot%3B%20calling%20on%20supporters%20to%20stay%20in%20their%20vehicles%20and%20continue%20swiftly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStay%20in%20your%20vehicles%20so%20we%20can%20reach%20there%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20urged%2C%20reiterating%20the%20necessity%20to%20press%20on%20without%20delay.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20here%20to%20bring%20Khan%20back.%20Let's%20move%20without%20delay%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20directed%2C%20reinforcing%20the%20singular%20focus%20on%20securing%20her%20husband's%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%2C%20led%20by%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20has%20been%20organising%20the%20march%20towards%20Islamabad%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20hold%20a%20protest%20at%20D-Chowk.%20The%20protest%2C%20which%20PTI%20describes%20as%20a%20movement%20for%20freedom%20and%20justice%2C%20has%20stirred%20political%20tensions%2C%20with%20party%20members%20and%20their%20supporters%20increasingly%20vocal%20about%20the%20arrest%20of%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20reported%20The%20Express%20Tribune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI's%20call%20to%20action%20is%20to%20gather%20at%20D-Chowk%2C%20despite%20government%20attempts%20to%20prevent%20the%20rally.%20The%20Interior%20Ministry%20has%20emphasised%20that%20no%20protests%20will%20be%20permitted%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20citing%20court%20orders%2C%20and%20warned%20of%20legal%20action%20against%20any%20violation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20related%20development%2C%20PTI%20leaders%20Aamir%20Dogar%20and%20Zain%20Qureshi%20were%20arrested%20by%20Punjab%20Police%20at%20the%20Qadirpurra%20Toll%20Plaza%20in%20Multan.%20The%20arrests%20have%20only%20heightened%20tensions%20as%20PTI%20proceeds%20with%20its%20plans%20for%20the%20protest.%20Despite%20the%20government's%20efforts%2C%20which%20include%20sealing%20key%20roads%20and%20setting%20up%20barriers%20around%20Islamabad%2C%20PTI%20leadership%20has%20remained%20firm%20in%20its%20stance.%20Gandapur%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20bring%20our%20private%20machinery%20to%20remove%20obstacles%20and%20reach%20Islamabad%2C%26quot%3B%20emphasising%20that%20nothing%20would%20deter%20their%20efforts%20to%20stage%20the%20protest%20at%20D-Chowk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20made%20preparations%20for%20the%20protest%20by%20heavily%20fortifying%20Islamabad%2C%20sealing%20key%20roads%20and%20setting%20up%20barriers%20across%20the%20city.%20Security%20forces%2C%20including%20Rangers%20and%20Frontier%20Constabulary%2C%20were%20deployed%20to%20sensitive%20areas%2C%20especially%20the%20Red%20Zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20restricted%20access%20to%20critical%20locations%20such%20as%20D-Chowk%20and%20Islamabad%20Airport%2C%20with%20containers%20placed%20along%20the%20routes%20leading%20into%20the%20capital.%20The%20measures%20have%20caused%20widespread%20disruption%2C%20with%20public%20transit%20halted%20and%20major%20roads%20blocked%2C%20leaving%20citizens%20unable%20to%20move%20freely%20across%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHospitals%20have%20been%20placed%20on%20high%20alert%20in%20anticipation%20of%20potential%20unrest%2C%20and%20terrorism%20warnings%20have%20been%20issued%20due%20to%20the%20threat%20of%20militants%20infiltrating%20the%20Pakistan-Afghanistan%20border.%20In%20preparation%20for%20the%20demonstration%2C%20PTI%20workers%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20pre-emptive%20arrests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20PTI%20members%2C%20including%20former%20MNA%20Nafisa%20Khattak%2C%20were%20detained%20late%20Friday%20night%2C%20while%20additional%20arrests%20occurred%20in%20Lahore%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20Punjab%2C%20The%20Express%20Tribune%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20counteract%20potential%20disturbances%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Interior%20has%20confirmed%20that%20internet%20and%20mobile%20data%20services%20may%20be%20suspended%20in%20high-risk%20zones.%20This%20is%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20the%20security%20of%20key%20areas%20and%20preventing%20the%20spread%20of%20information%20that%20could%20fuel%20unrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20security%20measures%20have%2C%20however%2C%20led%20to%20significant%20frustration%20among%20the%20public%2C%20as%20transportation%20systems%20and%20daily%20routines%20have%20been%20severely%20impacted%20by%20the%20widespread%20roadblocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20