t%3B90%20Armed%20Miscreants%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Manipur%20Police%20team%20that%20went%20to%20destroy%20illegal%20opium%20cultivation%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Kangpokpi%20district%20were%20stopped%20by%20%26quot%3B80-90%20armed%20miscreants%26quot%3B%20and%20forced%20to%20return%20without%20clearing%20the%20illegal%20farms%2C%20a%20police%20officer%20said%20in%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20team%20had%20a%20mix%20of%2025%20personnel%2C%20and%20volunteers%20from%20the%20Liangmai%20Naga%20tribe%20and%20five%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20carried%20only%20three%20assault%20rifles%20as%20it%20is%20a%20physically%20demanding%20and%20difficult%20task%20to%20destroy%20poppy%20farms%20with%20farm%20tools%20while%20also%20carrying%20AK-type%20guns%2C%20a%20source%20who%20has%20first-hand%20information%20about%20the%20incident%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20hold%20a%20weapon%20and%20also%20destroy%20poppy%20efficiently%20in%20such%20a%20sensitive%20area.%20The%20authorities%20should%20have%20deployed%20other%20forces%20along%20with%20the%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20police%20team%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20turn%20back%20when%20the%20armed%20miscreants%20tried%20to%20snatch%20the%20few%20guns%20the%20team%20had%2C%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20was%20remote%20and%20reinforcements%20would%20have%20taken%20a%20long%20time%2C%20so%20a%20decision%20was%20taken%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20joint%20team%2C%20the%20FIR%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20official%20confirmation%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20buzz%20in%20the%20security%20establishment%20in%20Manipur%20of%20a%20major%20operation%20involving%20central%20forces%20to%20clear%20new%20illegal%20opium%20poppy%20farms.%20The%20forces%20will%20retaliate%20if%20any%20armed%20miscreant%20threatens%20to%20stop%20the%20anti-poppy%20cultivation%20drive%20or%20fires%20at%20them%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frq3a5kag_kangpokpi-poppy-farm_625x300_24_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20their%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20from%20Manipur%20often%20include%20Kangpokpi%20district%20in%20many%20unrecognised%20hand-drawn%20maps%20used%20for%20social%20media%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKangpokpi%20is%20also%20the%20turf%20of%20the%20insurgent%20group%20Kuki%20National%20Front%20(KNF)%2C%20headed%20by%20ST%20Thangboi%20Kipgen%2C%20and%20this%20group%20is%20one%20of%20the%20over%20two%20dozen%20Kuki-Zo%20militant%20groups%20that%20have%20signed%20the%20controversial%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%2C%20which%20the%20Manipur%20government%20has%20been%20demanding%20to%20be%20scrapped.%20The%20SoO%20agreement's%20last%20renewal%20deadline%20was%20in%20February%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20society%20groups%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20have%20alleged%20the%20hand%20of%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%20in%20growing%20illegal%20opium%20poppy%20in%20areas%20dominated%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kangpokpi%20police%20chief%20in%20a%20flash%20message%20on%20November%2018%20ordered%20officers%20in%20charge%20of%20Kangpokpi%20and%20G%20Saparmeina%20police%20stations%20to%20destroy%20the%20illegal%20opium%20poppy%20farms%20in%20Makhan%20hill%20range%2C%20police%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%20The%20area%20of%20operation%20fell%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20police%20in%20G%20Saparmeina%2C%20some%2035%20km%20north%20of%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0