e%20a%20headwind%20to%20the%20labor%20market%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20deportations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETodd%20Buccholz%2C%20a%20former%20White%20House%20economist%20during%20the%20George%20H.W.%20Bush%20Administration%2C%20thinks%20Trump's%20immigration%20policies%20will%20have%20a%20mild%20economic%20impact%2C%20partly%20because%20he%20doubts%20immigration%20will%20fall%20over%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20important%20that%20the%20country%20recognize%20the%20aging%20of%20the%20population%2C%20the%20lower%20fertility%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20Buccholz%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20say%2C%20no%20one%20else%20is%20coming%20in%2C%20the%20gate%20is%20locked%20and%20no%20one%20else%20can%20play%20%E2%80%A6%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20shrinking%20and%20have%20more%20senior%20citizens%20and%20fewer%20people%20to%20support%20them.%20I%20think%20that%20raises%20real%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-immigration-workforce-deportations-migrants-economy-population-decline-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732455001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673552a1fa0140cdd56341be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-immigration-workforce-deportations-migrants-economy-population-decline-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22America's%20population%20could%20plunge%20as%20much%20as%2032%25%20if%20the%20US%20were%20to%20completely%20close%20its%20borders%2C%20one%20Brookings%20projection%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A162%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-immigration-workforce-deportations-migrants-economy-population-decline-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22