oring%20sessions%20and%20valuable%20industry%20connections%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99ve%20supported%20us%20through%20funding%20discussions%2C%20pitch%20deck%20management%2C%20and%20more.%20They%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20wind%20beneath%20our%20wings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssisting%20Vivek%20and%20Vani%20are%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Karthikeyan%20Gururaj%2C%20who%20also%20lost%20two%20of%20his%20pets%20to%20medical%20emergencies.%20For%20Karthikeyan%2C%20the%20startup%20was%20initially%20a%20client%20for%20technology%20platform%20development%20but%20he%20soon%20realised%20that%20the%20devices%20they%20were%20developing%20could%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268184%2Fdelhi-kitchen-for-paws-feed-stray-dogs-animals-food-divya-gurwara%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaved%20his%20dogs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20join%20their%20mission.%20The%20fourth%20key%20person%20to%20join%20them%20was%20S%20Rajkumar%2C%20who%20is%20pursuing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20biomedical%20design%20at%20IIT%20Madras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExam%20D%3A%20A%20non-invasive%20solution%20for%20accurate%20diagnoses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Vani%20and%20Vivek%20have%20three%20pet%20dogs%20each.%20As%20Vani%20argues%2C%20a%20major%20challenge%20in%20dealing%20with%20pet%20dogs%20is%20their%20high%20tolerance%20for%20pain%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20pet%20owners%20like%20her%20to%20recognise%20any%20real%20signs%20of%20discomfort.%20With%20a%20human%20child%2C%20you%20check%20their%20forehead%20to%20see%20if%20they%20have%20a%20fever%20and%20give%20them%20some%20soup.%20With%20dogs%2C%20however%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20touch%20their%20forehead%20and%20gauge%20whether%20they%20have%20a%20fever%20or%20not.%20Instead%2C%20you%20use%20devices%20like%20a%20rectal%20thermometer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVETiNSTANT%20replaced%20traditional%20rectal%20thermometers%20with%20a%20non-invasive%20device%20for%20diagnosing%20animal%20health.%20They%20also%20introduced%20a%20mobile%20app%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20pet%20parents%20to%20connect%20with%20veterinarians%20for%20timely%20diagnosis%20and%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-500x635.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vetinstant's%20non-invasive%20device%20for%20Pet%20Parents%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-500x635.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-236x300.jpg%20236w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-150x190.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942.jpg%20541w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22635%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20handheld%2C%20IoT-driven%2C%20at%20home%20diagnostic%20device%2C%20that%20unlike%20its%20wearables%20counterparts%2C%20provides%20pet%20parents%20exact%20data%20with%20range%20information%20for%20temperature%2C%20heart%20rate%20or%20SpO2%20(oxygen%20saturation)%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vivek.%20It%20took%20them%20about%20two%20years%20and%20four%20prototypes%20to%20arrive%20at%20their%20final%20product%20%E2%80%98Exam%20D%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cintegrated%20with%20our%20VETiNSTANT%20tracker%20app.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%