0encourage%20my%20patients%20to%20leave%20the%20hospital%20thoughts%20behind%20once%20they%20go%20home.%20Peace%20of%20mind%20is%20essential%20for%20recovery.%20Each%20patient%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20unique%2C%20like%20our%20fingers.%20Comparing%20their%20experience%20to%20others%20only%20makes%20the%20battle%20harder.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%99An%20angel%20for%20us%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20societal%20perceptions%20often%20deter%20people%20from%20seeking%20therapy%2C%20particularly%20for%20illnesses%20like%20cancer.%20Alpa%20challenges%20this%20mindset%3A%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20willingly%20seek%20counselling%20for%20marriage%20or%20divorce.%20Why%20not%20for%20cancer%2C%20where%20mental%20strength%20can%20be%20the%20key%20to%20a%20healthy%20fight%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20that%20many%20patients%20and%20caregivers%20hesitate%20to%20associate%20with%20her%20publicly%2C%20fearing%20the%20stigma%20of%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20heartbreaking%20that%20families%20worry%20more%20about%20societal%20opinions%20than%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20well-being%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CHealthcare%20professionals%20should%20also%20encourage%20counselling%20for%20patients%20with%20terminal%20illness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaregivers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332931%2Fnamarita-kathait-started-the-listening-circles-promote-mental-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprimarily%20require%20therapy%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20their%20journey%20is%20as%20challenging%20as%20the%20one%20with%20a%20physical%20illness.%20The%20pressure%20of%20providing%20the%20proper%20care%20for%20the%20patient%2C%20financial%20struggle%2C%20etc%2C%20also%20takes%20a%20toll%20on%20the