%20us%20when%20my%20father%20was%20battling%20a%20prolonged%20illness%20and%20during%20the%20final%20days%20of%20my%20elder%20brother%2C%20who%20was%20mentally%20challenged.%20Every%20time%20I%20called%20her%20during%20tough%20times%2C%20despite%20the%20hour%2C%20she%20always%20made%20sure%20that%20we%20had%20clarity%20and%20felt%20at%20peace%20after%20the%20conversation.%E2%80%9D%20Ketan%20is%20grateful%20for%20what%20Alpa%20has%20done%20and%20continues%20to%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMany%20patients%20ask%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20me%3F%E2%80%9D%20after%20their%20diagnosis.%20Alpa%20encourages%20them%20to%20instead%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CTry%20me!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20her%20own%20experiences%2C%20Alpa%20also%20believes%20emotions%20can%20correlate%20with%20certain%20illnesses.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20observed%20many%20breast%20cancer%20patients%20have%20unresolved%20%E2%80%98mothering%E2%80%99%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20either%20with%20their%20mothers%20or%20their%20children.%20While%20I%20respect%20medical%20science%2C%20my%20work%20has%20broadened%20my%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEncouraging%20empathy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFluent%20in%20seven%20languages%20%E2%80%94%20Hindi%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Tamil%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sign%20language%2C%20Alpa%20ensures%20her%20counselling%20is%20accessible%20to%20a%20diverse%20group%20of%20patients.%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20worked%20with%20a%20deaf%20and%20mute%20woman%20who%20was%20worried%20about%20losing%20her%20long%20hair%20to%20chemotherapy.%20Using%20simple%20actions%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20address%20her%20concerns.%20Unfortunately%2C%20many%20government%20hospitals%20lack%20resources%20for%20such%20communication%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20communication%2C%20Alpa%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20requirement%20of%20language%20for%20counselling.%E2%80%9D%20Most%20patients%20want%20to%20say%20a%20few%20words%20and%20be%20heard%2C%20which%20the%20doctor%20needs%20more%20time%20to%20listen%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20member%20of%20the%20International%20Death%20Doula%20Foundation%2C%20Alpa%20helps%20people%20arrange%20their%20final%20rituals%20once%20they%20have%20passed%20away.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20work%20in%20end-of-life%20counselling%20as%20loss%20and%20grief%20become%20our%20primary%20emotions.%20Once%2C%20a%20patient%20asked%20me%20to%20attend%20her%20funeral%20and%20be%20a%20shoulder%20to%20cry%20on%20for%20her%20mother%2C%20who%20was%20also%20battling%20cancer.%20I%20participated%20in%20the%20funeral%2C%20which%20is%20never%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alpa%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20was%20struggling%20to%20handle%20the%20loss.%20Now%2C%20with%20my%20mentors%E2%80%99%20advice%2C%20I%20can%20switch%20pretty%20quickly.%20I%20have%20provided%20counselling%20in%20the%20ICU%20as%20loneliness%20hits%20bad%20and%20people%20have%20passed%20away%20while%20talking%20to%20me.%20I%20always%20have%20a%20clear%20mind%20when%20I%20enter%20my%20home.%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20like%20switching%20on%20and%20off!%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-1-1732163252.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alpa%20wearing%20a%20wig%20to%20encourage%20other%20cancer%20patients.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%2