ce%20of%20sustainability%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20The%20Lodge%20at%20Wah%2C%20you%20name%20the%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eyou%20are%20in%20the%20mood%20for%2C%20and%20chances%20are%20it%20is%20grown%2C%20processed%2C%20brewed%20and%20served%20right%20on%20the%20land.%20During%20the%20tea%20tour%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20make%20an%20acquaintance%20with%20these%20different%20varieties%20which%20will%20give%20you%20an%20insider%20pass%20into%20the%20tea%20manufacturing%20process.%20Learn%20the%20nuances%20of%20tea%20production%2C%20including%20the%20processes%20of%20withering%2C%20rolling%2C%20fermenting%2C%20drying%2C%20and%20sorting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLodge-at-Wah-sustainable-travel-4-1732099435.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Lodge%20at%20Wah%20is%20a%20sustainable%20homestay%20in%20Palampur%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20that%20is%20built%20on%20a%20legendary%20tea%20estate%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLodge-at-Wah-sustainable-travel-4-1732099435.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLodge-at-Wah-sustainable-travel-4-1732099435-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLodge-at-Wah-sustainable-travel-4-1732099435-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLodge-at-Wah-sustainable-travel-4-1732099435-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLodge-at-Wah-sustainable-travel-4-1732099435-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381386%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Lodge%2