entist%20Interaction%20cum%20Field%20Day%E2%80%99%20organised%20by%20NRCM%2C%20where%20he%20learned%20about%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming.%20Inspired%20by%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20potential%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20switch%20from%20rice%20to%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20cultivation%20on%20his%20three-hectare%20plot%2C%20thus%20becoming%20a%20key%20case%20study%20of%20Dr%20Kumar.%20With%20technical%20guidance%20from%20NRCM%20and%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%2C%20he%20planted%20Swarna%20Vaidehi%20seeds%20in%20a%20nursery%20and%20later%20transplanted%20them%20into%20his%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20initial%20challenges%20with%20nutrient%20management%2C%20Dhirendra%20harvested%2048%20quintals%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20first%20season%2C%20earning%20a%20gross%20income%20of%20Rs%205.28%20lakhs%20and%20a%20net%20income%20of%20Rs%202.58%20lakhs.%20This%20was%20a%20dramatic%20improvement%20compared%20to%20the%20Rs%2060%2C000%20he%20earned%20from%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F324920%2Fbrothers-biodegradable-animal-friendly-rice-agri-waste-tableware-cutlery-plates-glass%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20rice%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20the%20same%20land%20in%20previous%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPolythene%20lining%20as%20a%20simple%20solution%20to%20water%20management%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20technique%20that%20further%20boosted%20Dhirendra%E2%80%99s%20success%20was%20polythene%20lining%20to%20prevent%20water%20loss%20from%20lateral%20seepage.%20Traditionally%2C%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farmers%20struggled%20to%20maintain%20consistent%20water%20levels%20in%20their%20fields%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20dry%20pre-monsoon%20months%20(March%20to%20May).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kumar%